    "description": "<p>AMAZON WEB SERVICES SINGAPORE PRIVATE LIMITED is a provider of remote computing services (also called web services) that together make up a cloud computing platform that is provided over the internet by Amazon.com. The most popular and well known of these services are Amazon EC2 and Amazon S3. The services are promoted as being centred around providing a large computing capacity, potentially many servers that are much faster and cheaper than actually having ones own datacentre.</p>    <p> </p>    <p> </p>  ",
